      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong>, and <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped onion</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 6-8 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1629717661985-x200.jpg",
