            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a pot with a matching lid with a generous drizzle of<strong> vegetable oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>cumin seeds</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until sizzling</p><p>Once the cumin seeds start to sizzle, carefully add your <strong>basmati rice</strong> and stir it all together</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1629717665876-x200.jpg",
