            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>turmeric</strong> and 250ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[320ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml] </span><strong>cold water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to the pot and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once cooked, remove from the heat and keep covered until serving – this is your <strong>turmeric rice</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
