        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>tamarind paste </strong>with 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[200ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up, then cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>paneer pathia</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
