    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> paneer pathia</strong> with the<strong> turmeric rice</strong> and <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>naans</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the<strong> chopped coriander</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
